summary:
An accomplished and results-focused professional with extensive experience leading large-scale programs for multi-national organizations. Derek has 20+ years of proven success delivering customer satisfaction through on-time, -budget, and -scope completion of transformation programs. 

As a strategic thinker he successfully articulates complex ideas in a transparent and simplified manner and takes an Enterprise approach to balancing stakeholder requirements. 

Derek is a leader who thrives in high performing cultures and gets organizations from “strategy to execution”.
